T_r
\left(1+\frac\lambda n\right)^n
\frac {n(n-1)(n-2)\cdots\{n-(r-1)\}}{1\cdot2\cdot3\cdots (r-1)r}\left(\frac\lambda n\right)^r
r\ge 1, T_0=1
\lim_{n\to\infty}T_r
\left(1+\frac\lambda n\right)^n
\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac {n(n-1)(n-2)\cdots(n-r+1)}{1\cdot2\cdot3\cdots (r-1)r}\left(\frac\lambda n\right)^r
=\frac{\lambda^r}{r!}\lim_{n\to\infty}\prod_{0\le s\le r-1}\left(1-\frac sn\right)=\frac{\lambda^r}{r!}
\lim_{n\to\infty}\left(1+\frac\lambda n\right)^n=1+\sum_{1\le r<\infty}\frac{\lambda^r}{r!}=\sum_{0\le r<\infty}\frac{\lambda^r}{r!}=e^\lambda
e=\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}(1+\frac1n)^n = \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{1}{n!}
